Communication Protocol

Direction Protocol Data Frequency
App → Sensor Hub SPI/I2C Query text + flags On demand
Sensor Hub → App SPI/I2C Response + metadata On demand
Sensor Hub → PMIC GPIO Power state changes Real-time
Sensor Hub → Cloud Wi-Fi/5G Anonymized logs (3-year cycle) Batch

The Integration Flow

```
USER SPEAKS "What is the freezing point of water?"
    ↓
Voice recognition (main SoC) → Converts to text
    ↓
App sends text to Sensor Hub via SPI
    ↓
Sensor Hub MCU runs ST-T1024:
    1. Intent Harvesting: "what is the freezing point of water"
    2. Ternary FIS → DOMAIN: PHYSICS (score: +1)
    3. FSM → Activate PHYSICS tile (<5 ns)
    4. Tiny Transformer → "0°C" (680 ns)
    5. FSM → Power down tile (0V)
    6. Result: "0°C" + "Energy is conserved"
    ↓
Sensor Hub sends response to App via SPI
    ↓
App displays response to user
    ↓
ENTIRE PROCESS: < 1 microsecond
```

Example Communication Code

```c
// Sensor Hub: Receive query from SoC
uint8_t spi_receive_buffer[256];
void SPI_IRQHandler(void) {
    // Read query from SPI
    spi_receive_buffer = SPI_Read();
    
    // Run ST-T1024
    QueryIntent intent = harvest_intent(spi_receive_buffer);
    char* response = st_t1024_run(&intent);
    
    // Send response back via SPI
    SPI_Write(response);
}
```

