6. Certification

The AET Advantage

Standard Domain ST-T1024 Compliance
ISO 26262 Automotive (ASIL-D) ✅ AET provides provable timing
IEC 61508 Industrial (SIL 3) ✅ FSM path fully auditable
DO-178C Aerospace ✅ FSM state transitions verifiable
IEC 62304 Medical ✅ Planned — deterministic by design

For smartphones, ISO 26262 alignment is particularly relevant — many smartphone components are already automotive-grade (e.g., Qualcomm's Snapdragon Auto).

Certification Path

```bash
# 1. Run formal verification
python3 validate_st_t1024.py --target arm --cycles 400

# 2. Generate certification documentation
